Package: entsoeapi.mcp
Title: MCP Server for the ENTSO-E Transparency Platform API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sándor", "Budai", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           email = "sbudai.ga@gmail.com")
Description: Provides a Model Context Protocol (MCP) server that exposes
    the 'entsoeapi' package as tools for LLM-enabled applications such as
    Claude Desktop. Allows querying European electricity market, load,
    generation, transmission, outages, and balancing data through natural
    language.
Depends: R (>= 4.2.0)
Imports:
    entsoeapi,
    mcptools,
    ellmer,
    lubridate,
    jsonlite
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/sbudai/entsoeapi.mcp
BugReports: https://github.com/sbudai/entsoeapi.mcp/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
